    "In Section 3.4 we detailed our in-prompt hallucination reduction efforts, but these will never reach zero.",
    "Hospital staff run the experiments, so they can correct the robot if it ever produces a hospitalrelated hallucination.",
    "This is also why we do not provide the SDS with any personal information like patient appointment schedules -we do not want to cause confusion.",
    "In a real deployment, prompt poisoning could be an issue.",
    "A bad actor can manipulate the system to output incorrect responses through dialogue."
